{
  "stem": "24346.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this particular cousin, two of her other sisters, I don't know what happened, because they all lived in one house when they told them to get out to the market.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's where, from this one, things where remembered, what people told me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, remember, I told you before, Rumkowski offered to supply work product to the Germans, or the Germans asked-- either way, there were established resorts.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we got assigned jobs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They assigned me and my mother to a job where clothes from people came back on trains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It came back, we had to sort out these clothes-- shirts to shirts, jackets to jackets, slacks to slacks, overcoats to overcoats.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of the clothes were recognized from people what were in the ghetto-- meaning, if they took out a transport, this was the clothes from these people, And some were bullet-ridden and bloody.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got an idea what's happening to the people what left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, obviously, they were killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lot of clothes came in, a lot of clothes that we had constantly work, in that particular resort, we separated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was older from me, [INAUDIBLE]-- I had an uncle, Avrumci, which I marked on your list.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very good bricklayer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, very few Jews, before the war, were bricklayers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow, I don't know how-- he was my uncle, I don't know how he got this trade-- but he is a master, was a master, rather, in that trade.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the ghetto, they needed people-- the thing, because there were some bombed-out houses from the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they created a building department.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember the head was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Goodman. ?] And my uncle went, registered himself-- he's a bricklayer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Fine, we could use people.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
